WEBVTT

00:00:00.440 --> 00:00:02.790
Good morning, family! Praise the Lord, it

00:00:02.790 --> 00:00:02.800
is

00:00:02.800 --> 00:00:05.710
day 45 of praying in a row. I know I

00:00:05.710 --> 00:00:05.720
have

00:00:05.720 --> 00:00:08.830
skipped a couple, but we are pretty much dead on

00:00:08.840 --> 00:00:11.870
45, so praise the Lord. I have some

00:00:11.880 --> 00:00:14.589
things on my heart today. I was

00:00:14.599 --> 00:00:16.590
praying and the Lord showed me some

00:00:16.600 --> 00:00:19.150
things in the spirit to pray about today,

00:00:19.160 --> 00:00:20.830
so we're going to get right to it.

00:00:20.840 --> 00:00:23.230
I want to backtrack a little

00:00:23.240 --> 00:00:24.750
bit and talk about when the

00:00:24.760 --> 00:00:27.189
Lord told me that He was bringing the

00:00:27.199 --> 00:00:30.550
cure for cancer

00:00:30.550 --> 00:00:30.560
to

00:00:30.560 --> 00:00:32.470
the world and the body of Christ. He said

00:00:32.480 --> 00:00:34.670
this has plagued generations for too

00:00:34.680 --> 00:00:37.869
long now. He said, 'Son, the

00:00:37.879 --> 00:00:41.350
cure for cancer is out

00:00:41.350 --> 00:00:41.360
there.'He

00:00:41.360 --> 00:00:45.990
said that evil men in

00:00:45.990 --> 00:00:46.000
power

00:00:46.000 --> 00:00:49.830
have held it back for

00:00:49.840 --> 00:00:53.029
material gain, and He said, 'I'm

00:00:53.039 --> 00:00:56.150
going to crush them, the ones that have

00:00:56.160 --> 00:01:00.509
held back the cure.'I saw a

00:01:00.519 --> 00:01:03.830
man

00:01:03.840 --> 00:01:06.830
in a laboratory mixing this

00:01:06.840 --> 00:01:11.109
stuff up, and he found

00:01:11.119 --> 00:01:14.950
a greater cure for

00:01:14.960 --> 00:01:19.310
cancer. It was

00:01:19.320 --> 00:01:21.590
a daily supplement that you

00:01:21.600 --> 00:01:24.870
take to prevent it and cure it.

00:01:24.880 --> 00:01:27.789
The Lord gave

00:01:27.799 --> 00:01:30.830
supernatural wisdom to this person.

00:01:30.840 --> 00:01:31.910
While

00:01:31.920 --> 00:01:35.069
he was in this laboratory

00:01:35.079 --> 00:01:36.830
mixing this

00:01:36.840 --> 00:01:39.870
supplement, the Lord showed me

00:01:39.880 --> 00:01:41.190
that it was just a little bit of this

00:01:41.200 --> 00:01:42.630
and a little bit of that. People

00:01:42.640 --> 00:01:44.230
have told me, 'Oh, it's Ivermectin'and all this

00:01:44.240 --> 00:01:47.350
other stuff, but that is not what I saw. I saw

00:01:47.360 --> 00:01:50.429
a supplement that was a preventative and

00:01:50.439 --> 00:01:53.630
a cure coming in the

00:01:53.640 --> 00:01:56.670
future. Whenever I was praying, the

00:01:56.680 --> 00:02:02.270
Lord showed me to pray for Robert

00:02:02.270 --> 00:02:02.280
F.

00:02:02.280 --> 00:02:04.789
Kennedy Jr.. He told me to intercede for Robert

00:02:04.789 --> 00:02:04.799
F.

00:02:04.799 --> 00:02:07.029
Kennedy Jr. because attacks were coming

00:02:07.039 --> 00:02:10.029
against him because of the freedom that

00:02:10.039 --> 00:02:12.589
he wants to bring to the FDA and the

00:02:12.599 --> 00:02:16.110
food industry to expose the darkness

00:02:16.120 --> 00:02:19.030
that has been in place

00:02:19.040 --> 00:02:21.630
worldwide. It started out of America

00:02:21.630 --> 00:02:21.640
and

00:02:21.640 --> 00:02:23.229
went into Europe and

00:02:23.239 --> 00:02:25.030
Asia. The Lord

00:02:25.040 --> 00:02:26.670
showed me it had

00:02:26.680 --> 00:02:29.550
tentacles for corruption, poisoning

00:02:29.560 --> 00:02:31.270
people

00:02:31.280 --> 00:02:33.910
through our foods

00:02:33.910 --> 00:02:33.920
and

00:02:33.920 --> 00:02:37.350
environmental factors. There's a lot of

00:02:37.360 --> 00:02:43.910
corruption intended to depopulate the

00:02:43.920 --> 00:02:46.790
world. The Lord showed me not

00:02:46.800 --> 00:02:51.390
