00:02:51.400 --> 00:02:55.390
expose a lot of the

00:02:55.400 --> 00:02:58.070
darkness. There are roots of things

00:02:58.080 --> 00:03:00.509
that are not all good,

00:03:00.519 --> 00:03:02.270
so I'm not sitting here on the Kennedy bandwagon,

00:03:02.280 --> 00:03:05.630
but he has

00:03:05.640 --> 00:03:10.030
an assignment to fulfill to expose

00:03:10.040 --> 00:03:12.990
darkness that the enemy has tried to

00:03:13.000 --> 00:03:16.470
bring to shorten human

00:03:16.470 --> 00:03:16.480
life.

00:03:16.480 --> 00:03:18.949
There are plenty of

00:03:18.959 --> 00:03:22.430
resources on this Earth to sustain

00:03:22.440 --> 00:03:27.070
life beyond 8 billion or 14 billion.

00:03:27.080 --> 00:03:28.390
Whatever they say

00:03:28.390 --> 00:03:28.400
about

00:03:28.400 --> 00:03:30.670
depopulation agendas—those

00:03:30.670 --> 00:03:30.680
are

00:03:30.680 --> 00:03:32.589
evil things.

00:03:32.599 --> 00:03:35.110
The Lord

00:03:35.120 --> 00:03:38.110
knew what we needed before our

00:03:38.120 --> 00:03:40.229
little peanut brains tried to figure

00:03:40.239 --> 00:03:42.789
it out.

00:03:42.799 --> 00:03:45.350
God

00:03:45.350 --> 00:03:45.360
is

00:03:46.910 --> 00:03:46.920
all-sufficient.

00:03:48.589 --> 00:03:48.599
It

00:03:48.599 --> 00:03:52.509
didn't

00:03:52.519 --> 00:03:54.949
shock

00:03:54.959 --> 00:03:56.550
Him that there are 8 billion

00:03:56.560 --> 00:03:59.149
people.

00:04:00.840 --> 00:04:04.670
God is a God of surplus. This Earth

00:04:04.670 --> 00:04:04.680
is

00:04:04.680 --> 00:04:06.630
never a shock to Him.

00:04:06.640 --> 00:04:09.550
It's

00:04:09.560 --> 00:04:13.069
greed and demonic,

00:04:13.079 --> 00:04:18.310
reprobate thinking. These

00:04:18.310 --> 00:04:18.320
men in

00:04:18.320 --> 00:04:21.469
high power

00:04:21.469 --> 00:04:21.479
are

00:04:21.479 --> 00:04:23.390
influenced by demonic

00:04:23.400 --> 00:04:25.950
spirits.

00:04:25.960 --> 00:04:27.350
I can't mention their names,

00:04:27.360 --> 00:04:30.909
but

00:04:30.919 --> 00:04:33.150
these men are buying up farmland

00:04:33.150 --> 00:04:33.160
and

00:04:33.160 --> 00:04:36.590
causing

00:04:36.600 --> 00:04:38.310
corruption

00:04:38.320 --> 00:04:42.070
for material

00:04:42.080 --> 00:04:45.390
gain, joining up with the

00:04:45.400 --> 00:04:47.469
devil. I have seen

00:04:47.479 --> 00:04:49.870
