00:05:19.160 --> 00:05:20.749
They

00:05:20.759 --> 00:05:22.469
don't listen to the poor, they listen to

00:05:22.479 --> 00:05:24.990
the rich, and the rich have power. That

00:05:24.990 --> 00:05:25.000
is

00:05:25.000 --> 00:05:26.950
why God wants to raise up godly

00:05:26.960 --> 00:05:30.430
